{
    "name": "Saboteur",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Saboteur",
            "type": "section",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Gamemastery Guide",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 246",
                        "alt": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 246",
                        "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq01zq7"
                    },
                    "page": 246
                }
            ],
            "html": "Saboteurs excel at infiltration, using it to perform destructive acts, whether they are the physical destruction of a valuable object or obstructing important political proceedings. Unlike those of spies, the motivations of saboteurs is not to steal information, but rather to sow chaos among their enemies.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Humanoid</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"14\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Society</a></u>)</b>: DC 16"
        },
        {
            "name": "Villains",
            "type": "section",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Gamemastery Guide",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 246",
                        "alt": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 246",
                        "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq01zq7"
                    },
                    "page": 246
                }
            ],
            "html": "Villains pursue selfish and cruel goals, trampling over anyone foolish or purehearted enough to stand in their way."
        }
    ],
